verbose_text: Pretreatment with GDF11 significantly improved cardiac morphology and function in diabetes, concomitant with decreased arrhythmia severity, infarct size, CK-MB, LDH and 15-F2tisoprostane release, increased SOD activity and autophagy level.
evidence: CK-MB, LDH and 15-F2tisoprostane release, increased SOD
